                  <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
                  <p>Lady Diana Milner was the wife of Sir William Mordaunt Milner (1754-1811) of Nun Appleton in North Yorkshire. The daughter of Humphrey and Mary Pitfield Sturt of Crichel More, Dorset, she died in Exeter, Devon, on January 17, 1805, and was interred in Exeter Cathedral.</p>
